extends page-head

block content

  // Page Wrapper
  #page-wrapper
    // Header
    header#header.alt
      h1
        a(href='index.html') Ani
      nav#nav
        ul
          li.special
            a.menuToggle(href='/')
              span Home
    // Banner
    section#banner
      .inner
        h2 Ani
        p
          | Making your home life better.

      a.more.scrolly(href='#one') Learn More
    // One
    section#one.wrapper.style1.special
      .inner
        header.major
          h2
            | Ani is designed to integrate into existing
            br
            | living spaces with minimal disruption.
          p
            | A clean, modern design ensures that units look good without dominating the room.
            br
            | Always there when you need it but never intrusive when you want time to yourself,
            br
            | Ani is the perfect roommate.
        ul.icons.major
          li
            span.icon.fa-diamond.major.style1
              span.label Beautiful
          li
            span.icon.fa-heart-o.major.style2
              span.label Helpful
          li
            span.icon.fa-code.major.style3
              span.label Powerful
    // Two
    section#two.wrapper.alt.style2
      section.spotlight
        .image
          img(src='images/pic01.jpg', alt='')
        .content
          h2
            | Simply powered by awesome tech
          p
            | Driven by Microsoft Kinect and Cortana technologies, and able to hook into the vast computing power of the Azure cloud, Ani is smarter than a tree full of owls.
            br
            br
            | Suitable for both home and office environments, Ani is an inexpensive and fully scalable platform.
      section.spotlight
        .image
          img(src='images/pic02.jpg', alt='')
        .content
          h2
            | Affordable
          p
          | The Ani system has been refined and optimised to make home-wide implementations easy and affordable.
      section.spotlight
        .image
          img(src='images/pic03.jpg', alt='')
        .content
          h2
            | A much needed helping hand
          p
            | Ani provides personalised assistance when you need it most, whether it be friendly reminders, music while you shower or help in an emergency.
    // Three
    section#three.wrapper.style3.special
      .inner
        header.major
          h2 User stories
          p
            | Ani can be a personal assistant, companion, security guard, or babysitter. All you need to do is ask!
        ul.features
          li.icon.imagebox
            img(src="/images/ryan.gif")
          li.icon
            h3 Ryan
            p
              | Ryan likes to know when his kids get home from school, so Ani sends him an sms message when they walk in the door.
          li.icon
            h3 Stacy
            p
              | Stacy likes to check to the news and any emails before work. Ani follows her around the house reading them out while she gets ready. This evolves to music duty in the afternoons.
          li.icon.imagebox
            img(src="/images/stacy.gif")
          li.icon.imagebox
            img(src="/images/peter.gif")
          li.icon
            h3 Peter
            p
              | Peter is getting on in years, so Ani keeps him company and helps out if he ever needs a hand. Family or emergency services are just one 'HELP!' away.
    // CTA
    section#cta.wrapper.style4
      .inner
        header
          h2 Coming soon
          p
            | Return home to register interest!
        ul.actions.vertical
          li
            a.button.fit.special(href='/') Home
    // Footer
    footer#footer
      ul.icons
        li
          a.icon.fa-twitter(href='#')
            span.label Twitter
        li
          a.icon.fa-facebook(href='#')
            span.label Facebook
        li
          a.icon.fa-instagram(href='#')
            span.label Instagram
        li
          a.icon.fa-dribbble(href='#')
            span.label Dribbble
        li
          a.icon.fa-envelope-o(href='#')
            span.label Email
      ul.copyright
        li Â© Pitchblack
        li
          | Ani

